Package: CESD
Type: Package
Title: CESD data processing scripts
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Peter Kraska
Maintainer: Peter Kraska <peter.kraska@dfo-mpo.gc.ca>
Description: This package is a set of scripts written to Extend, Transform, and 
    Load  (ETL) data being gathered withing the Coastal Ecosystem Science Division
    (CESD). Generally, these are based on older scripts that are no longer 
    maintained in an effort to make them more user friendly and maintainable. 
    
    Other scripts might find their way into this package over time.
